{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3a6aa99e22","title":"关于军队文化大革命的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d391041692","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":27,"articleId":"3a6aa99e22"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"aa048f8141","name":"夺权","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6e534520dc","type":"title","text":"关于军队文化大革命的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"3a6aa99e22"},{"id":"2801e4c7f1","type":"paragraph","text":"一、我认为十三个军区不要同时搞，要有先有后","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"3a6aa99e22"},{"id":"96295c4678","type":"paragraph","text":"二、地方文化大革命正在猛烈开展，夺权斗争还在剧烈进行，我们军队要支持地方革命左派进行夺权斗争，因此军队和地方文化大革命要分开。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"3a6aa99e22"},{"id":"271f328ebd","type":"paragraph","text":"三、现在国际上帝、修、反正在利用我们文化大革命继续大搞反华活动，如苏联在镇压学生，新疆边界飞机活动多了，地面部队也在调动。凡是前线的大军区要警惕，要有所准备，如济南、南京、福州、广州、昆明等地区，所以文化大革命要稍推一下，将来一定要搞的，顾大局","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"3a6aa99e22"}],"page":{"id":"d2ae39e381","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"3a6aa99e22","start":288,"end":288}}}},"__N_SSG":true}